OL,3,CConfidence risk in Omagh Bombing
OL,4,CInquiry amid special advocate request
OL,6,FThere is a risk of damage to
OL,7,Fconfidence in the Omagh Bombing
OL,8,FInquiry if the bereaved families are
OL,9,Frefused their request for a special
OL,10,Fadvocate for closed hearings, it has
OL,11,Fbeen argued.
OL,13,FThe families say a special advocate
OL,14,Fwill be able to represent their
OL,15,Finterests in closed hearings where
OL,16,Fevidence is deemed sensitive,
OL,17,Fincluding in terms of national
OL,18,Fsecurity.
