OL,3,CConfidence risk in Omagh Bombing
OL,4,CInquiry amid special advocate request
OL,6,FThe probe is examining whether the
OL,7,F1998 atrocity in the Co Tyrone town
OL,8,Fcould have been prevented.
OL,10,FSome 29 people, including a woman
OL,11,Fpregnant with twins, were killed when
OL,12,Fthe Real IRA exploded a car bomb on a
OL,13,Fbusy Saturday afternoon in Omagh.
OL,15,FThe inquiry is sitting this week in
OL,16,FBelfast to hear arguments over the
OL,17,Fapplication for special advocates for
OL,18,Fthe survivors and bereaved families.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
