OL,6,FHugh Southey KC, acting for a number
OL,7,Fof survivors and bereaved families,
OL,8,Falso contended former chief constable
OL,9,FSir Ronnie Flanagan would appear to be
OL,10,Fat "an advantage" over them.
OL,12,FHe also raised that counsel for the
OL,13,Finquiry would "have to look after the
OL,14,Finterests of a number of people who
OL,15,Fare excluded from the closed
OL,16,Fproceedings, who have potentially
OL,17,Fquite conflicting interests".
