OL,4,CInquiry amid special advocate request
OL,6,FIan Skelt KC, acting for Sir Ronnie,
OL,7,Fsaid his client is "entirely
OL,8,Fsympathetic" to the requests of the
OL,9,Ffamilies and acknowledges why they
OL,10,Fseek and why they feel that there is a
OL,11,Fneed for the appointment of special
OL,12,Fadvocates.
OL,14,FHe said Sir Ronnie does not seek a
OL,15,Fspecial advocate for himself, but
OL,16,Facknowledged that having been chief
OL,17,Fconstable at the time of the bombing,
OL,18,Fhe had the authority at that time to
OL,19,Fview much of the closed material.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@LO]
