OL,6,FHowever, Mr Skelt said if Sir Ronnie
OL,7,Fis excluded from the closed processes,
OL,8,Fhe "may have to ask for some person to
OL,9,Frepresent his interest in closed
OL,10,Fprocess beyond the assistance that
OL,11,Fwould be given by the inquiry legal
OL,12,Fteam".
OL,14,FAlan Kane KC, representing another
OL,15,Fgroup of survivors and bereaved
OL,16,Ffamilies, said they would like their
OL,17,Fown special advocate for closed
OL,18,Fhearings.
OL,26,@pD@DOUtD@EO]
