OL,6,F"Their wish would be to see all the
OL,7,Frelevant evidence after 26 years,
OL,8,Fhowever if there must be closed
OL,9,Fmaterial, then we say that it should,
OL,10,Fwhere possible, be kept to a minimum,
OL,11,Fand if judgments are to be made then
OL,12,Fclose calls must fall on the side of
OL,13,Fdisclosure rather than being hidden
OL,14,Ffrom our families' view," he said.
