OL,6,FFintan McAleer, who represents another
OL,7,Fgroup of survivors and bereaved
OL,8,Ffamilies, said they endorsed the
OL,9,Fsubmissions made so far.
OL,11,FInquiry chair Lord Turnbull asked Mr
OL,12,FMcAleer about a point made in written
OL,13,Fsubmissions that the "deep mistrust
OL,14,Fand suspicion of the state that exists
OL,15,Fin this country will never be fully
OL,16,Fallayed unless it's confirmed that
OL,17,Fevery single document and piece of
OL,18,Finformation is placed into the open".
OL,26,@uD@VOUzD@dO]
