OL,6,F"We're simply trying to convey the
OL,7,Faspiration of the core participants we
OL,8,Frepresent is that this inquiry should
OL,9,Fbe in public in everything that it
OL,10,Fdoes, we accept there is a limitation
OL,11,Fon that, and that paragraph is an
OL,12,Fattempt to address that."
OL,14,FMeanwhile Michael Mansfield KC, who
OL,15,Frepresents the family of the late
OL,16,Fcampaigner Laurence Rush, whose wife
OL,17,FElizabeth was killed in the bomb, said
OL,18,Fthey are not asking for a special
OL,19,Fadvocate to be appointed for them.
